title: Blood amber is a portal into dinosaur times ... and an ethical minefield
description: When it comes to dinosaurs, many of us think of towering skeletons dominating the atriums of the world's great natural history museums.

title: Thousands of protesters gather in Bangkok, demanding reform
description: Thousands gathered in Thailand this weekend at a rally calling for reform, which culminated Sunday with a group attempting to march to the Monarch's Privy Council, next to the Royal Palace, to deliver their demands -- an explosive and unprecedented move in a country that reveres the monarchy.

title: Trump says he has approved a deal for purchase of TikTok
description: President Donald Trump said Saturday he has approved a deal between TikTok's parent company, ByteDance, and Oracle, though it is unclear whether it will be enough to avert restrictions on TikTok that are scheduled to go into effect Sunday evening.

title: Torch-inspired Tokyo skyscraper to become Japan's tallest building
description: A 390-meter-high (1,279 feet) skyscraper inspired by a flaming torch is set to become Japan's tallest building when it opens in 2027.

title: Two people were killed and 14 were wounded in Rochester shooting, police say
description: Two people were killed and fourteen others were wounded during a shooting in Rochester, New York, police said early Saturday morning.
